<HEADLINE>
SPORTS COLUMN: TAKING THE MEASURE OF A YOUNG TRACK STAR 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (Repeats to add art advisory.)  (ART ADV: Photos NYT 6,7 are being sent to NYT photo clients.
Nonsubscribers can purchase one-time rights by calling 888-603-1036
or 888-346-9867.) 
