<P>
   JANETLEIGH-PSYCHO _ Janet Leigh's biggest claim to fame cost
exactly one week of her life. That's how long it took Alfred
Hitchcock to film ``Psycho's'' memorable and horrific shower scene
_ a riveting montage (70 separate shots unfolding in roughly three
minutes). On Wednesday, Leigh brings ``Psycho'' to audiences for
free at the Fox summer film series. We talk to her about working
with Hitchcock, making the movie and its affect on her life.
(BLongino, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 30. MOVED.
